I got a letter from Jenny,

1396
01:59:14.898 --> 01:59:19.194
wondering if I could come down
to Savannah and see her,

1397
01:59:19.235 --> 01:59:21.821
and that's what I'm doing here.

1398
01:59:21.905 --> 01:59:24.532
