Hey, I kept a scrapbook
of your clippings and everything.

1416
02:00:43.611 --> 02:00:45.238
There you are.

1417
02:00:46.990 --> 02:00:48.110
And this, I got you running.

1418
02:00:51.161 --> 02:00:53.329
I ran a long way,

1419
