1423
02:01:16.311 --> 02:01:21.566
'cause I was messed up
for a long time, and...

1424
02:01:24.360 --> 02:01:25.987
- Hey.
- Hi.

1425
02:01:26.196 --> 02:01:27.197
Hey, you.

1426
02:01:28.364 --> 02:01:31.367
- This is an old friend from Alabama.
- How do you do?

1427
